creator: Jin-geon Hyun
description:
LibriVox recording of Short Stories (단편 소설) by Jin-geon Hyun (현진건). Read in Korean by Jessie Yun. 한국 소설가 현진건이 쓴 소설들 중 3개를 뽑은 모음집. (요약: 윤지수) 3 short stories by Korean writer Hyun Jin-geon. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

Download M4B (32MB)
